<header>
  <a class="hdr-logo-link" href="../index.html" title="Zurück zum Englisch-Lernzentrum"><img src="../assets/logo_hellweg.png" alt="Logo der Hellweg-Realschule Unna-Massen" style="cursor:pointer"/></a>
  <h1>If-Sätze Typ 1</h1>
  <p class="sub">Bedingungssätze Typ 1 – reale Bedingungen für die Zukunft mit <i>if + Simple Present</i> und <i>will-Future</i></p>
</header>

<div class="container">
  <section class="rules-combined">
    <div class="quiz-divider" style="margin:0 0 16px"><span>⚡ Regeln auf einen Blick</span></div>
    <div class="rc-grid">

      <div class="rc-card c-green">
        <div class="rc-card-topbar"></div>
        <div class="rc-card-num">1</div>
        <div class="rc-card-body">
          <div class="rc-card-label">✅ Aufbau (Bildung)</div>
          <div class="rc-formula">
            <span class="fc fc-sig">if</span><span class="fc-pair"><span class="fc-plus">+</span><span class="fc fc-subj">Subj.</span></span><span class="fc-pair"><span class="fc-plus">+</span><span class="fc fc-verb">Simple Present</span></span><span class="fc-punct">,</span><span class="fc fc-subj">Subj.</span><span class="fc-pair"><span class="fc-plus">+</span><span class="fc fc-do">will</span></span><span class="fc-pair"><span class="fc-plus">+</span><span class="fc fc-verb">Grundform</span></span>
          </div>
          <div class="rc-rule">If-Satz Typ 1 hat <b>zwei Teile</b>:<br>• <b>if-Teil</b>: nennt die Bedingung – Verb im Simple Present<br>• <b>Hauptsatz</b>: nennt die Folge – will + Grundform</div>
          <div class="rc-examples-new">
            <span class="hl-sig">If</span> you <span class="hl-verb">send</span> me a message, <span class="hl-do">I'll</span> <span class="hl-verb">come</span>.<br>
            <span class="hl-sig">If</span> it <span class="hl-verb">rains</span>, we <span class="hl-do">won't</span> <span class="hl-verb">play</span>.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="rc-card c-blue">
        <div class="rc-card-topbar"></div>
        <div class="rc-card-num">2</div>
        <div class="rc-card-body">
          <div class="rc-card-label">📐 if-Satz: Simple Present</div>
          <div class="rc-formula">
            <span class="fc fc-sig">if</span><span class="fc-pair"><span class="fc-plus">+</span><span class="fc fc-subj">Subj.</span></span><span class="fc-pair"><span class="fc-plus">+</span><span class="fc fc-verb">V (Simple Present)</span></span>
          </div>
          <div class="rc-rule">Im if-Teil steht <b>Simple Present</b>: <i>I/you/we/they + Grundform</i>, <i>he/she/it + Grundform + s</i>.<br><b>Verneinung:</b> don't / doesn't + Grundform.<br><span style="font-size:12px">⚠️ <b>NIE will</b> im if-Satz!</span></div>
          <div class="rc-examples-new">
            If you <span class="hl-verb">study</span> hard …<br>
            If she <span class="hl-verb">comes</span> early …<br>
            If it <span class="hl-neg">doesn't</span> <span class="hl-verb">rain</span> …
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="rc-card c-amber">
        <div class="rc-card-topbar"></div>
        <div class="rc-card-num">3</div>
        <div class="rc-card-body">
          <div class="rc-card-label">🎯 Hauptsatz: will-Future</div>
          <div class="rc-formula">
            <span class="fc fc-subj">Subj.</span><span class="fc-pair"><span class="fc-plus">+</span><span class="fc fc-do">will</span></span><span class="fc-pair"><span class="fc-plus">+</span><span class="fc fc-verb">Grundform</span></span>
          </div>
          <div class="rc-rule">Im Hauptsatz steht das <b>will-Future</b>: <i>will + Grundform</i> (für alle Personen gleich).<br><b>Kurzform:</b> I'll, you'll, she'll …<br><b>Verneinung:</b> won't (= will not) + Grundform.</div>
          <div class="rc-examples-new">
            … <span class="hl-do">I'll</span> <span class="hl-verb">come</span>.<br>
            … <span class="hl-do">she'll</span> <span class="hl-verb">help</span> us.<br>
            … we <span class="hl-do">won't</span> <span class="hl-verb">play</span>.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="rc-card c-indigo">
        <div class="rc-card-topbar"></div>
        <div class="rc-card-num">4</div>
        <div class="rc-card-body">
          <div class="rc-card-label">🔄 Reihenfolge &amp; Komma</div>
          <div class="rc-formula">
            <span class="fc fc-sig">if-Teil</span><span class="fc-punct">,</span><span class="fc fc-do">Hauptsatz</span><span class="fc-punct">·</span><span class="fc fc-do">Hauptsatz</span><span class="fc fc-sig">if-Teil</span>
          </div>
          <div class="rc-rule">Der if-Teil kann <b>vorne ODER hinten</b> stehen.<br>• <b>if vorne</b> → <b>Komma</b> nach dem if-Teil<br>• <b>if hinten</b> → <b>kein Komma</b></div>
          <div class="rc-examples-new">
            <b>If it rains, we won't play.</b><br>
            <b>We won't play if it rains.</b><br>
            <span style="font-size:11px;color:#6b7280">← gleiche Bedeutung, andere Stellung</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="rc-card c-red">
        <div class="rc-card-topbar"></div>
        <div class="rc-card-num">5</div>
        <div class="rc-card-body">
          <div class="rc-card-label">❌ Häufiger Fehler</div>
          <div class="rc-formula">
            <span class="fc fc-sig">if</span><span class="fc-pair"><span class="fc-plus">+</span><span class="fc fc-do" style="text-decoration:line-through">will</span></span>
          </div>
          <div class="rc-rule"><b>NIE will im if-Teil!</b> Im if-Teil steht <b>immer Simple Present</b>.<br>Auch nicht: doesn't will, won't … im if-Teil.<br><span style="font-size:12px">⚠️ Auch <i>he tells</i> ist falsch im Hauptsatz – dort kommt <i>will tell</i>.</span></div>
          <div class="rc-examples-new">
            <span style="color:#b83a22;text-decoration:line-through">If it will rain, we will stay.</span><br>
            <b style="color:#16a34a">If it rains, we will stay.</b>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="rc-card c-teal">
        <div class="rc-card-topbar"></div>
        <div class="rc-card-num">6</div>
        <div class="rc-card-body">
          <div class="rc-card-label">⏱ Wann benutze ich es?</div>
          <div class="rc-formula" style="flex-wrap:wrap;gap:5px 4px">
            <span class="fc-tz">reale Bedingung</span>
            <span class="fc-tz">Zukunft</span>
            <span class="fc-tz">möglich</span>
          </div>
          <div class="rc-rule">If-Sätze Typ 1 nutzt du für <b>reale, mögliche Bedingungen in der Zukunft</b>: Was wird passieren, <b>wenn</b> eine Bedingung erfüllt ist?</div>
          <div class="rc-examples-new">
            <i>If we win, we'll celebrate.</i><br>
            <span style="font-size:11px;color:#6b7280">← realistisch: wir können gewinnen, dann feiern wir.</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

